title: Decline Of Western Civilization Part 1 (divx transcode)
description:
SOURCE:
SVCD VHS Capture transcoded from the 3-part Torrent located 
at http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/3298038/

The source video is a very good quality capture, perhaps 
from a professional quality SVHS VTR. Please keep in mind 
however that the source material wasnt 35mm or 16mm or some 
digital format, it was good ol' VHS (this film hasnt yet made 
it to digital officially) so dont be surprised by some image 
instability and bleeding. There is very little in the way 
of static or banding.

The image has not been cropped at all, to preserve as much of 
malco23's original capture as possible.

ENCODE:
DIVX 5.x/6.x 
Video - 648x488 25fps progressive. 
Audio - 48000Hz 320kbps CBR Stereo MP3.
Should be compatible with almost all DivX capable DVD players
